channel.title: Anyone help me get server online on team-viewer? (I'm port forwarded)
channel.description:
I've been trying hours on hours to get this up... It's a 317 pi source. Client came with the source, i changed the ip in client.java. Port 43594 is forwarded on my no-ip, and i know my no-ip and port forwarding works because I have other applications using them. But when my friend tries to play my webclient, says "Error connecting to server". I compiled after changing ip, and have the server running...
Reply here and ill pm you TV info and maybe you can help me out :/
